To make the programs:
$ make

Program results
$ ./pi
pi with 100000000 steps is 3.141593 in 0.405651 seconds

$ ./pi_omp_private
pi with 100000000 steps is 3.141593 in 0.168258 seconds

$ ./pi_omp_teams
<not implemented yet>

$ ./pi_omp_threads
<not implemented yet>

